Generate detailed milestones for the candidate's transition from {{ current_role }} to {{ target_role }} ({{ experience_level }} level) over {{ estimated_duration_months }} months.

Candidate Profile Context:
{{ context }}

Roadmap Phases:
{% for phase in roadmap_phases %}
Phase {{ phase.phase_number }}: {{ phase.title }}
Duration: {{ phase.duration }}
Description: {{ phase.description }}
{% endfor %}

Construct a list of milestones. Return only a JSON object:
{
  "milestones": [
    {
      "id": "m1",
      "title": "Milestone Title",
      "description": "Milestone Description",
      "start_week": 1,
      "end_week": 4,
      "estimated_hours": 40,
      "prerequisite_skills": ["Skill A"],
      "expected_outcome": "Outcome",
      "completion_status": "NOT_STARTED"
    }
  ]
}

Ensure the response contains only the raw, valid JSON object. Do not add markdown backticks, notes, or explanations.
